1
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:45,100
[My Heroic Husband]

2
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,900
[Episode 32]

3
00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:50,900
When we go back to Jiangning, we can even buy your stand,

4
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:54,200
let alone your steamed buns. It's no big deal to us.

5
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:59,100
If you want to have a store, we can open one for you.

6
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:00,800
You can choose the location.

7
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:03,000
At that time, you won't have to work so hard

8
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:06,500
through the wind and rain by then.

9
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:09,600
Wen Xing, let's go.

10
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:12,000
Goodbye.

11
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:37,000
I have drawn the people away who have been watching you.

12
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,500
What should we do tomorrow night?

13
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:42,400
Fang Tian Lei and Shao Xian Ying

14
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,800
have called all the people together

15
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:46,500
from the eight camps to the wedding tomorrow night.

16
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:50,400
The city must be weakly defended tomorrow night.

17
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:53,400
This is the only chance for us to attack.

18
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:56,000
Please go out of the city

19
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:59,800
and deliver the message to Dong Dao Fu.

20
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,200
Yes.

21
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:20,400
Everything has been well arranged.

22
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:24,000
Is everything done?

23
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,600
Nothing will go wrong.

24
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:29,598
I will bury some explosives near each city gate.

25
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:31,600
Fang Qiong, you can skip the wedding.

26
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,100
Just find an excuse.

27
00:03:33,100 --> 00:03:36,000
You'll have to work hard and watch for any movements on the watchtower.

28
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,800
I'll have Zheng Biao and Wang Jin

29
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:40,800
guard the south gate and north gate respectively so as to be ready for the battle.

30
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,400
Yes.

31
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:48,600
But I feel queer to do so on Xi Gua's wedding day.

32
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:51,200
We have no other choice.

33
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,800
Don't worry.

34
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,800
If everything goes well tomorrow,

35
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:57,700
then they will lead a happy life hereafter.

36
00:03:57,700 --> 00:04:01,600
If not, that means Xi Gua has married the wrong man.

37
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,700
We can just kill Ning Yi.

38
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,700
Is this plan workable?

39
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:12,400
I didn't receive your signal last time,

40
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,600
I guessed that you didn't make it.

41
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:18,400
Now, the Secret Investigation Department has suffered great losses.

42
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:20,800
If we put all our eggs in one basket…

43
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:24,600
Does Ning Yi have a sure card?

44
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,300
Please don't worry, General. 
[Granary Storehouse of Lin'an]

45
00:04:26,300 --> 00:04:28,500
All the bandits will gather together at the camp on the wedding day.

46
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,200
The city will be weakly defended.

47
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:32,200
He knows what to do.

48
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:35,400
General, please just wait for the timing.

49
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,600
Holy Master.

50
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,600
- Open the door.
-Yes.

51
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:46,200
It's dry and well-ventilated.

52
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:48,500
This has met all the requirements.

53
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:50,600
Zheng Biao, well done.

54
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,500
I'm flattered, Holy Master.

55
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,300
Great.

56
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:01,300
Send these explosives to the city gates

57
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:03,200
and bury them later.

58
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:06,000
Make sure each of our people is equipped with a blunderbuss

59
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,200
- and have them shift guards all night.
- Yes.

60
00:05:08,200 --> 00:05:12,000
And, if anything goes wrong tonight,

61
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:15,600
you know what to do with Ning Yi, right?

62
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:18,200
- Yes, understood!
- Yes, understood!

63
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,700
Let's go.

64
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:23,600
[Divorce agreement - Husband and Wife. Su Tan'er]

65
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,300
My dear.

66
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:27,800
I know what you're thinking.

67
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:32,100
But now you will marry someone else.

68
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,700
I think it's better for us

69
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:39,700
to get a formal divorce before that.

70
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:41,200
Then you can be relieved

71
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,500
and do what you should.

72
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,200
I'm serious.

73
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:52,800
Now all the people in Lin'an need you.

74
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:55,100
I understand it.

75
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:59,700
I also know this wedding is fake.

76
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:03,900
I'm sorry to make you go through all this.

77
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:05,500
I'm fine.

78
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:10,200
As a man, you should do something.

79
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,400
Moreover, from the bottom of my heart,

80
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:15,200
I think you are so much more than a matrilocal husband.

81
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,600
You deserve a bigger world.

82
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,100
So,

83
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:32,400
please sign the divorce agreement.

84
00:08:14,400 --> 00:08:16,800
[Husband - Ning Yi]
[Wife - Su Tan'er]

85
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:41,400
Here, let me see.

86
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:47,400
I tailored this wedding robe for you myself.

87
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:49,800
It really fits you perfectly.

88
00:08:49,800 --> 00:08:51,800
But due to limited time,

89
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,700
it's not as delicate as

90
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:56,000
what you wore on our wedding day.

91
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,800
Why are you looking at me?

92
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,700
I'm really fine!

93
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:09,600
Seeing you in the wedding robe,

94
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:12,300
reminds me of the time when we got married.

95
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:17,200
And remember you said that you wanted to take me on a honeymoon.

96
00:09:23,100 --> 00:09:24,600
Tan'er,

97
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,700
I'll make it up

98
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,500
to you one day.

99
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,800
It's kind of late now.

100
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:13,200
Why haven't you done your hair?

101
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:22,800
A wedding is a lifetime big event for a girl.

102
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,300
It's normal to be nervous.

103
00:10:24,300 --> 00:10:26,900
Don't worry. We're all here for you.

104
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:30,600
Your uncle and I will stay with you.

105
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:35,800
But when I go out dressed like this,

106
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:38,200
everyone may laugh at me.

107
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:42,400
As the commander of Badao Camp, It's so embarrassing.

108
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:45,300
You look so pretty.

109
00:10:45,300 --> 00:10:47,400
No one dares to laugh at you.

110
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:50,400
If there are any who laugh at you, your uncle and I won't forgive them.

111
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,600
If only your parents were still alive.

112
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:04,600
They would have been happy to see you get married.

113
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:12,000
For a girl from an ordinary family, her mother would pierce her ears at two or three.

114
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,700
Your mother passed away when you were little.

115
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:16,400
No one has taught you how to dress up.

116
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,500
Come.

117
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,800
Do I have to be pierced?

118
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:37,500
Wearing this wedding dress,

119
00:11:37,500 --> 00:11:40,000
it will make you prettier with earrings.

120
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:43,800
It only happens once in a lifetime.

121
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,800
You don't even fear battles.

122
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:47,600
Why are you afraid now?

123
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:51,000
Who's afraid?

124
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:05,470
[Happiness]

125
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:16,800
Our Xi Gua is so pretty.

126
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,200
Let me out.

127
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:36,000
Let me out!

128
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,400
Is there someone?

129
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:42,200
Help! I need go out!

130
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:44,000
Is there someone?

131
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:49,000
Let me out! Let me out!

132
00:12:57,100 --> 00:12:59,300
She can't marry Ning Yi.

133
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:06,000
I don't agree!

134
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:13,100
I want to see her.

135
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:15,700
I want to see her.

136
00:13:15,700 --> 00:13:17,800
Let me out!

137
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,800
[Fang Manor]

138
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:51,000
Get everything up.

139
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,700
Sit down!

140
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:17,200
Although Xi Gua is my adopted daughter,

141
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,600
she's no different from my own.

142
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:24,800
It's your wedding day today.

143
00:14:24,800 --> 00:14:27,300
That's the dowry I prepared for you.

144
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,700
From now on,

145
00:14:34,700 --> 00:14:37,200
you should lead a happy life.

146
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:40,400
Ning Yi, I will be the first one to stand out

147
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:42,800
if you treat her badly.

148
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,600
Okay. Holy Master has granted his reward.

149
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,200
Let's get started right away.

150
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:50,300
We can't miss the auspicious time.

151
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:54,890
[Lin'an]

152
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:01,200
[Viewpoint of Lin'an]

153
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:19,800
Now is the auspicious time.

154
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:22,600
Today, under the witness of the Holy Master and Empress,

155
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:25,100
Counselor Ning married into Badao Camp

156
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:26,400
and became a matrilocal husband of Commander Liu.

157
00:15:26,400 --> 00:15:28,400
Now, it's time to go to the bridal chamber!

158
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,800
Okay!

159
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:34,200
Go to the bridal chamber!

160
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:36,800
What are you doing, guys?

161
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:39,000
Do you think we're still in the mountains?

162
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:40,200
We're in the city now.

163
00:15:40,200 --> 00:15:41,800
It would be inappropriate if we don't have any ceremony.

164
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:43,600
Yes.

165
00:15:46,800 --> 00:15:48,200
Perform the formal wedding ceremony!

166
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:51,400
How could we forget it on Xi Gua's wedding day?

167
00:15:51,400 --> 00:15:53,000
Yes, the formal ceremony!

168
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,500
The formal ceremony!

169
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,800
We will do it according to our tradition.

170
00:15:57,800 --> 00:15:59,700
Go prepare it!

171
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:02,100
Yeah, sure.

172
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:39,000
The ceremony begins!

173
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,500
First, bow to Master Guan.

174
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:43,300
We brothers from eight camps stick to loyalty and righteousness.

175
00:16:43,300 --> 00:16:44,600
Only with death does our course end.

176
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:48,000
If you become a traitor, you will be cut through by swords and torn apart by carts.

177
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:50,800
Today, Ning Yi married into Badao Camp, and from now on,

178
00:16:50,800 --> 00:16:54,400
we should share happiness and difficulties together.

179
00:16:54,400 --> 00:16:56,200
Second, bow to the broadsword.

180
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:58,800
This sword was left by Xi Gua's father.

181
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:00,700
It's like you are bowing to your father-in-law.

182
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:03,800
Hope you can be of the same mind

183
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:06,600
and can overcome any difficulties in the future.

184
00:17:08,300 --> 00:17:10,800
Bow to each other.

185
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,400
The ceremony is done!

186
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:31,500
Great! Great!

187
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:34,700
Great! Great!

188
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:37,400
You will be a family from now on.

189
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:40,200
Ning Yi, now I will leave Xi Gua to you.

190
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:43,600
You have to treat her well from now on.

191
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:49,200
She had never fallen in love with someone for all these years.

192
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:53,000
Ning Yi, you must not let her down.

193
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:56,400
Can you do it?

194
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,700
He can, Aunt.

195
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:40,400
My Lady.

196
00:18:59,000 --> 00:19:00,800
Drink!

197
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:02,400
Come on. Bottoms up!

198
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:19,700
You two. May I propose a toast?

199
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:21,500
You don't deserve that.

200
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:27,200
Since you married Commander Liu, we can't do anything to you.

201
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:31,600
But in the future,

202
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:33,800
if you fall into our hands again…

203
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:37,300
What's wrong with you?

204
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:38,600
What?

205
00:19:38,600 --> 00:19:40,200
What's wrong?

206
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:45,000
What are you doing?

207
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,400
Are you rising in rebellion?

208
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:48,800
It's Xi Gua's wedding day.

209
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:51,600
You guys should act well today.

210
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:53,400
Let's go, Counselor.

211
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,400
Let's go and have a drink over there.

212
00:19:54,400 --> 00:19:57,200
What are you looking at? I will poke your eyes out.

213
00:19:58,400 --> 00:20:00,200
-Clean it up. Hurry!
- No problem.

214
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,600
- Let's drink ourselves.
- Let's drink ourselves.

215
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:04,100
Come on, Counselor. Come on, Counselor.

216
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:05,400
Let's drink now.

217
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,900
Good wine.

218
00:20:11,700 --> 00:20:12,900
Congratulations, Counselor.

219
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:14,400
Come on, everybody. Bottoms up!

220
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:16,000
Yeah.

221
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:18,400
- Come, cheers!
- Come on.

222
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:20,300
Come on.

223
00:20:20,300 --> 00:20:21,800
- Come on!
- Fill it up.

224
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:24,800
Counselor, it's not good if you drink like that!

225
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:26,800
I still have something to do later.

226
00:20:26,800 --> 00:20:28,200
He has to go to the bridal chamber!

227
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:29,800
He's got something serious to do tonight.

228
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:31,800
I think he's having ulterior motives.

229
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:34,600
The reason why he stays awake is that

230
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:38,800
he will work from inside with Dong Dao Fu tonight.

231
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,300
Keep your voice down.

232
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:42,100
- If he dares to do so…
- Cheers!

233
00:20:42,100 --> 00:20:44,700
I will kill him tonight.

234
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:53,200
Holy Master. A toast from we three.

235
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:55,200
Enough. Go find someone else.

236
00:20:55,200 --> 00:20:56,700
He won't drink tonight.

237
00:20:56,700 --> 00:20:58,800
Yes. Go.

238
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:07,600
Ning Yi is a generous man.

239
00:21:07,600 --> 00:21:10,400
Hope he won't let Xi Gua down.

240
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:12,000
He dare not.

241
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:16,000
Leave me alone.

242
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,700
Go there. Drink with them.

243
00:21:17,700 --> 00:21:18,600
I won't drink too much tonight.

244
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:20,000
Okay. Let's go.

245
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,000
Take care.

246
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,500
Let's go.

247
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:26,400
Bottoms up!

248
00:21:26,400 --> 00:21:28,000
Let's drink.

249
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:21,000
Come on. Give me more.

250
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:23,300
Come on, let's drink.

251
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,600
Come on, cheers.

252
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:30,600
- Let's drink.
- Okay.

253
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:17,000
Bottoms up!
[Happiness]

254
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:24,600
Counselor, we will escort you to the bridal chamber.

255
00:23:24,600 --> 00:23:25,500
Let's go, Counselor.

256
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:27,200
- Let's go.
- It's time.

257
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:28,800
Xuanwei Camp also sucks!

258
00:23:28,800 --> 00:23:30,400
Yeah. They all suck!

259
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:32,000
Look at him! And him!

260
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,100
Let's go, too.

261
00:23:33,100 --> 00:23:34,600
Yeah. Okay.

262
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:36,600
Let's go.

263
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:52,000
Get up.

264
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:02,700
Xian Ying, go take some rest.

265
00:24:02,700 --> 00:24:04,800
Act on our plan.

266
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,600
Hurry.

267
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:15,400
Come on.

268
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:18,400
Come on.

269
00:25:08,200 --> 00:25:12,400
Counselor, you have to treat Commander Liu well in the future.

270
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:14,500
Although this is your second marriage,

271
00:25:14,500 --> 00:25:18,200
Commander Liu has never liked anyone.

272
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:19,000
Yeah.

