00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,600
You're so lucky, Counselor.

274
00:25:20,600 --> 00:25:22,200
But she just likes you.

275
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:24,200
What can we do about it?

276
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:26,800
Everyone has his own taste.

277
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:31,000
You must treat her well in the future.

278
00:25:32,200 --> 00:25:34,800
If you dare to treat her badly,

279
00:25:34,800 --> 00:25:37,300
we'll be the first ones to kill you.

280
00:25:37,300 --> 00:25:40,000
- Yeah.
- Yeah!

281
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,400
All right.

282
00:25:41,400 --> 00:25:43,600
You can go back now. I've arrived.

283
00:25:43,600 --> 00:25:46,200
Yeah.

284
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:48,600
The wedding night!

285
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:50,200
Let's go! Go!

286
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:52,500
Every minute of the wedding night counts!

287
00:25:52,500 --> 00:25:53,800
Let's go back and drink!

288
00:25:53,800 --> 00:25:54,800
Let's drink!

289
00:25:54,800 --> 00:25:56,700
Let's drink until dawn.

290
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:06,200
[Granary Storehouse of Lin'an]

291
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:22,200
This knockout powder given by Ning is so effective!

292
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,400
Cut it out!

293
00:26:23,400 --> 00:26:26,000
Hurry up. Get changed!

294
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:39,100
This-This outfit looks weird.

295
00:26:39,100 --> 00:26:41,000
Are you serious? You still pay attention to your image now?

296
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:43,600
Of course. We will be killed if we're recognized.

297
00:26:43,600 --> 00:26:45,000
We won't.

298
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,400
I've observed their movements between their shifts.

299
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:50,000
You just need to follow me and don't say anything.

300
00:26:50,000 --> 00:26:54,100
Heroes, what about us?

301
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:56,800
I only drugged four bandits. There are no clothes for you.

302
00:26:56,800 --> 00:26:59,800
But… We will be recognized if we push the cart there.

303
00:26:59,800 --> 00:27:01,400
Yeah, we didn't put on any disguise.

304
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:03,900
It's like we're going to suicide.

305
00:27:03,900 --> 00:27:05,600
I've never seen those who're afraid of death like you.

306
00:27:05,600 --> 00:27:07,800
But… I'm kidding.

307
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:12,400
After we finish the task, you will come with the goods.

308
00:27:13,200 --> 00:27:14,700
Good idea!

309
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,500
May you succeed!

310
00:27:18,300 --> 00:27:19,800
Come back early!

311
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:22,100
Good luck with the task! Be careful!

312
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:24,100
Achieve academic success!

313
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:25,900
Break a leg! Come on!

314
00:28:08,039 --> 00:28:10,699
My Lady, are you still in the mood for a novel?

315
00:28:10,699 --> 00:28:13,199
We still don't know what's going on between Young Master and that woman.

316
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:17,200
If he dares to fail you, I will kill him!

317
00:28:19,700 --> 00:28:21,600
He won't.

318
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,700
Xi Gua,

319
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:49,200
I'm afraid you'll have to rough it tonight.

320
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:13,200
Stop!

321
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:17,200
Second Camp is on duty! First Camp goes back for rest!

322
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:18,800
You're late.

323
00:29:20,600 --> 00:29:24,400
That's because we took care of our needs on the way.

324
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:29,100
"There are many things I want to say."

325
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:32,100
I'm asking you! The password for tonight.

326
00:29:32,100 --> 00:29:34,400
"There are many things I want to say."

327
00:29:51,900 --> 00:29:55,000
"Please take care and not suffer from hunger and cold."

328
00:29:58,900 --> 00:30:02,200
The password is, "Please take care and not suffer from hunger and cold."

329
00:30:04,800 --> 00:30:06,600
Guys, let's go back for a rest!

330
00:30:06,600 --> 00:30:08,200
Okay!

331
00:30:08,200 --> 00:30:10,300
The rest of the evening watch is relying on you. Keep an ear to the ground.

332
00:30:10,300 --> 00:30:12,000
It's Commander Liu's wedding tonight.

333
00:30:12,000 --> 00:30:14,500
I heard that the enemy will attack.

334
00:30:14,500 --> 00:30:15,800
Okay, sure.

335
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:17,100
Let's go.

336
00:30:17,960 --> 00:30:19,798
Thank you for your hard work!

337
00:30:19,800 --> 00:30:22,700
- Thank you!
- Thank you!

338
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:26,000
What happened?

339
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,800
How did you know the password?

340
00:30:27,800 --> 00:30:31,000
They are the last two lines in the ancient poetry of Traveling over and over again.

341
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,300
"There are many things I want to say.

342
00:30:32,300 --> 00:30:34,400
Please take care and not suffer from hunger and cold."

343
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:37,100
It sounds weird. But that's what they wrote.

344
00:30:37,100 --> 00:30:40,800
Brother Shen, the time you've spent studying has not been wasted at all!

345
00:30:40,800 --> 00:30:41,600
Really.

346
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:43,900
Not until one is up against a practical problem to be solved does one realize how little they have read.

347
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:48,000
I wonder if he was hungry when he wrote this.

348
00:30:52,500 --> 00:30:54,200
- Get out.
- Come on.

349
00:30:54,200 --> 00:30:57,300
Hurry up! Hurry up!

350
00:31:20,200 --> 00:31:22,500
[Lin'an]

351
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:27,400
It's so stuffy.

352
00:31:27,400 --> 00:31:29,200
I can't even see the stars.

353
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:31,600
I've arranged it properly. Once they enter the city,

354
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:34,200
they will explode into pieces.

355
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:38,800
If Ning Yi is a spy and colludes with Dong Dao Fu,

356
00:31:38,800 --> 00:31:41,000
I will show no mercy to him.

357
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:53,700
Xi Gua, where did you buy the sunflower seeds?

358
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:56,200
It's so raw.

359
00:31:56,200 --> 00:31:57,400
So what?

360
00:31:57,400 --> 00:31:59,600
I can't taste it anyway.

361
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:01,100
I've been used to being hungry.

362
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:03,200
It's already good enough to have food.

363
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,200
You were also born of poor parentage.

364
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:10,400
No wonder you asked me to take back the grains and save the poor.

365
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:12,200
You were always hungry when you were little.

366
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:13,800
My father was down and out in other places.

367
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:15,800
My mother was alone and conceived me.

368
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:18,600
At that time, she couldn't afford a watermelon.

369
00:32:18,600 --> 00:32:22,500
Later, when I was born, she named me Xi Gua. (Xi Gua means watermelon)

370
00:32:22,500 --> 00:32:25,800
Although she still couldn't afford it, by naming me Xi Gua,

371
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:27,800
she'd feel like she has a watermelon every day.

372
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:31,200
Later my father came back, but we still suffered from hunger.

373
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:34,400
So, we could only become bandits.

374
00:32:34,400 --> 00:32:38,700
Have you ever thought about doing something else?

375
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:43,000
Like, you can do embroidery at our Su's.

376
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:45,600
Are you kidding me?

377
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:48,200
Now, I take charge of a whole camp!

378
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:51,200
How could I leave them alone and do something else?

379
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:53,700
You can bring them along.

380
00:32:55,800 --> 00:32:58,000
Enough. Thank you for your kindness.

381
00:32:58,000 --> 00:33:01,000
You just think it is not a permanent solution to live such a life.

382
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:03,000
My Aunt thought the same.

383
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:05,600
So she always wanted me to get married.

384
00:33:05,600 --> 00:33:09,000
But my father wanted to retire and live a peaceful life.

385
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:11,800
But he didn't expect that he'd be framed by corrupt officials

386
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:13,600
accusing him of treason.

387
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:16,000
He ended up losing his life.

388
00:33:17,500 --> 00:33:19,800
My mother died from sickness when I was little.

389
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:22,000
I hardly remember anything about her.

390
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:24,300
I was brought up by my father.

391
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:27,200
So I was very sad when he died.

392
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,600
His name was Liu Da Biao.

393
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:30,500
So I call myself that, too.

394
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:32,800
He followed my uncle and was so kind to him.

395
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:34,500
He'd listen to everything my uncle said.

396
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:37,200
So I chose to follow my uncle, too.

397
00:33:37,200 --> 00:33:39,800
Later, the people who heard the name Liu Da Biao

398
00:33:39,800 --> 00:33:44,000
thought he was still alive and came to Lin'an with the Holy Master.

399
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,400
You know what?

400
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:51,200
My father was quite awesome when he was young.

401
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:54,400
Although you are also very good,

402
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:56,600
you still can't compare to him.

403
00:33:57,300 --> 00:33:59,300
I dare not.

404
00:33:59,300 --> 00:34:03,400
My father taught me to be faithful and reasonable when I was little.

405
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:06,200
I only get to use strength if I can't win against them.

406
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:08,900
He was right.

407
00:34:09,700 --> 00:34:11,600
He just wanted to earn a living

408
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:13,400
and never thought about hurting anyone.

409
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:15,200
He was so loyal to my uncle.

410
00:34:15,200 --> 00:34:17,200
When those corrupt officials sent people to hunt him down,

411
00:34:17,200 --> 00:34:19,200
he said he'd take it all by himself

412
00:34:19,200 --> 00:34:20,400
and asked my uncle to leave with me.

413
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,400
You know it.

414
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:23,000
They just wanted to kill him.

415
00:34:23,000 --> 00:34:24,900
Being reasonable wouldn't have worked anyway.

416
00:34:24,900 --> 00:34:28,000
There's no other choice but to fight them.

417
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,800
Thinking about my father's kindness to him,

418
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,900
my uncle has always spoiled me.

419
00:34:32,700 --> 00:34:36,100
Actually, about Bao Wen Han's issue, he didn't believe you.

420
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:37,800
But I said I liked you.

421
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:39,400
So he couldn't punish you.

422
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:42,000
As for my aunt, it's because

423
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:44,400
she was afraid she'd fail my father's trust.

424
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:46,800
So she had to see us get married.

425
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,200
That's how it is.

426
00:34:48,200 --> 00:34:50,600
Can you two understand it?

427
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:53,600
We… Of course, we can.

428
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:58,800
But… we have put you in such big trouble.

429
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:01,100
What are you going to do then?

430
00:35:01,100 --> 00:35:02,300
It's nothing.

431
00:35:02,300 --> 00:35:05,500
My father told me that friends should be loyal to each other.

432
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:07,200
I thought about it before.

433
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:10,800
If this doesn't work, I will threaten my uncle with my own life.

434
00:35:10,800 --> 00:35:13,600
I didn't expect that you can be saved by a fake marriage.

435
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:15,300
What a good deal!

436
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:20,000
Xi Gua,

437
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:23,100
did you ever think that

438
00:35:23,100 --> 00:35:29,600
the Holy Master was determined to go on this path from the very beginning?

439
00:35:30,200 --> 00:35:31,600
No.

440
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:34,600
He just hates those corrupt officials doing evil

441
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:37,000
because they killed my father.

442
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,900
You denied it so fast.

443
00:35:39,600 --> 00:35:42,100
Even you don't believe it either, right?

444
00:35:47,000 --> 00:35:49,100
Uncle is kind to me.

445
00:35:49,100 --> 00:35:53,000
I will help him win this battle in Lin'an no matter what.

446
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,700
What if you can't?

447
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:59,200
It doesn't matter.

448
00:35:59,200 --> 00:36:01,000
If you lose,

449
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:03,800
Chen Fan and you can just surrender for amnesty.

